<p>Well, almost all ideas are &quot;viral&quot; in that you can spread them by communicating them to others, so the meme (the idea that explaining jokes is annoying) does counter the first by preventing the spread/belief in it. There's nothing anomalous about anything in this SCP or the counter-meme, but that's perfectly fine because a &quot;meme&quot; isn't actually inherently anomalous, despite what many on the site believe.</p>
